== About me

I am currently a first year postgraduate student, affiliated with the [https://diggers.ai/ DIG lab]. My advisors are Profs. [https://wenli-vision.github.io/ Wen Li] and [http://lxduan.info/ Lixin Duan].

I was previously a undergraduate student at the [http://cs.ahu.edu.cn/ Anhui University].

== Research

I am currently exploring the video editing and understanding, both theory and application.

In particular, I focus on the video super resolution and video inpainting.

